GV author [Filip Stojanovski](https://globalvoicesonline.org/author/filip-
stojanovski/) was
[interviewed](http://niemagazin.blogspot.com/2011/02/fb.html) [MKD] for the TV
show _Nie_ (“We”) on the topic of [“Kale, Internet, political parties,
Facebook!? Whose fault is
it?”](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/02/15/macedonia-violent-inter-
ethnic-incident-on-skopje-fortress/), where he spoke about the importance of
citizen media and Global Voices. The show also included a segment of [Ethan
Zuckerman's](https://globalvoicesonline.org/author/ezuckerman/) TED
[talk](http://www.ted.com/talks/lang/eng/ethan_zuckerman.html).

